title: This Game Is Too Realistic
description: This Game Is Too Realistic Manhua Starting with a shelter, tricking players into work for free, I am the administrator and chief customer service executive of Wasteland ONLINE——Chu Guang. After I accidentally opened a high-tech shelter after traveling into the post-apocalyptic world, I began to recruit “players” to be my slav- lackeys! Let them kill monsters so I can level up? TOO EASY! Come join me as I build the strongest base in an apocalyptic world full of mutants and monsters! The Game Is Too Real , 这游戏也太真实了, Zhe Youxi Ye Tai Zhenshile
